    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 B32 power plant equipped with individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS variable valve timing. Power is managed via a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and delivered to the rear wheels through a factory variable M-differential lock. The chassis has been proactively addressed with rear subframe reinforcement plates and features upgraded Bilstein dampers paired with refreshed control arm bushings for precise lateral stability and sharp turn-in. Recent mechanical maintenance includes a comprehensive valve lash adjustment and rod bearing replacement, ensuring internal engine longevity. While showing minor cosmetic wear consistent with its age, the vehicle maintains excellent mechanical integrity and offers a pure, analog driving experience with a linear power band and exceptional throttle response.",
