    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2017 Lexus GX 460 Premium, a vehicle that perfectly balances rugged capability with refined comfort. The exterior is finished in a striking Starfire Pearl that still holds a deep, brilliant shine. While you will find a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small, superficial scratch near the rear wheel well, the body is straight and free of any major dings. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of craftsmanship. The Ecru leather upholstery is in excellent shape, showing only light creasing on the driver's side bolster, and the genuine mahogany wood trim remains vibrant and crack-free. This is a non-smoker vehicle with no pet odors. Every electronic component, from the intuitive navigation system to the tri-zone climate control, operates exactly as it should. Mechanically, this SUV is top-tier. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a thick folder of records to prove it. The 4.6L V8 engine provides smooth, effortless power, and the 4WD system engages flawlessly. We recently fitted a new set of all-season tires and performed a comprehensive multi-point inspection. If you are looking for a dependable, luxury family hauler that has been treated with genuine care, this GX 460 is ready for its next chapter.",
